---

<Layout title="Build Winning Product Strategies & Bring Them to Market - SP Consulting">
  <Navigation />

  <main class="pt-20">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <section class="bg-primary text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Build Winning Product Strategies & Bring Them to Market</h1>
        <p class="text-xl">We partner with you to define, develop, and launch successful products.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Main Content Section */}
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50"> {/* Added a light background for contrast */}
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
        <div class="space-y-16">

          {/* Approach Section */}
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Our Approach to Product Success</h2>
            {/* Left-aligned paragraph */}
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
              Effective product management requires a holistic view. We help organizations navigate the complexities of product strategy, development, and market launch by focusing on key interconnected areas. Our experienced consultants work alongside your team to build robust processes, foster data-driven decisions, and accelerate your time-to-market.
            </p>

            {/* Diagram */}
            <div class="mb-12">
              <img
                src="/assets/product-management-diagram.png"
                alt="Product Management Core Areas Diagram"
                class="w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto rounded-lg"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 text-center">
                Our comprehensive framework considers all critical factors for product success.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Key Pillars Section */}
          <div class="mt-16"> {/* Adjusted top margin */}
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">Key Pillars of Our Product Strategy Framework</h2>
             {/* Using lg:grid-cols-3. Alternative: md:grid-cols-2 avoids empty slot but creates 3/2 layout */}
             <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
              {pillars.map(pillar => (
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm"> {/* Use white bg on gray main bg */}
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
                    <span class="mr-2">{pillar.icon}</span> {/* Placeholder Icon */}
                    {pillar.title}
                  </h3>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 list-disc list-inside pl-2"> {/* Added slight padding */}
                    {pillar.points.map(point => (
                      <li>{point}</li>
                    ))}
                  </ul>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Common Hurdles Section */}
          <div class="mt-20"> {/* Increased top margin for better separation */}
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Overcoming Common Product Development Hurdles</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Many organizations face significant challenges in bringing products to market efficiently. If these issues sound familiar, our program management expertise can help streamline your processes:
            </p>
            {/* Restyled challenges list container */}
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm mb-8">
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 list-disc list-inside">
                {challenges.map(challenge => (
                  <li>{challenge}</li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
             <p class="text-gray-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              We provide structured approaches, clear methodologies (Agile, Waterfall, Hybrid), resource management strategies, and effective team collaboration frameworks to address these program management obstacles.
            </p>
          </div>

          {/* Why Partner Section */}
          <div class="mt-20"> {/* Increased top margin */}
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">Why Partner with SP Consulting?</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
              <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                 <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                   {/* Replace with actual SVG icon */}
                   <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
                 </div>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Proven Expertise</h3>
                 <p class="text-gray-600">Years of experience driving product success and navigating complex launches across diverse industries.</p>
               </div>
               <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                 <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                   {/* Replace with actual SVG icon */}
                   <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" /></svg>
                 </div>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Tailored Approach</h3>
                 <p class="text-gray-600">Customized product strategies and program solutions that fit your unique market context and goals.</p>
               </div>
               <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                 <div class="bg-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                   {/* Replace with actual SVG icon */}
                   <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
                 </div>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Results-Driven</h3>
                 <p class="text-gray-600">Focused on delivering tangible improvements, clear ROI, and measurable product success metrics.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Call to Action Section */}
          <div class="text-center pt-12"> {/* Added padding top */}
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Ready to elevate your product strategy and execution?</p> {/* Added intro sentence */}
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors text-lg"
            >
              Discuss Your Product Challenges
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>